{"tid":2352770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：美方與其關心12名港人的死活 不如關心35萬因武漢肺炎死去的美國公民","createTime":"2021-01-04T08:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T09:52:24.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"dda9484b4585abc8ee7454407d7847b83fb94470","tid":2352770,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:54:58.000Z","msg":"回應蓬佩奧就12港人案對中方批評 外交部促停止抹黑<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩表示，就12名港人的案件，中國司法機關依法辦案，美方無權干涉。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩在外交部例行記者會，回應美國國務卿蓬佩奧批評中國共產黨迫害12名港人時表示，中國是法治國家，有法必依，違法必究，敦促美方停止對中國的誣蔑抹黑，停止借香港問題干涉中國內政，停止干涉中國司法主權。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩又說，美國的新型冠狀病毒疫情已造成2千多萬人確診，35萬多人死亡，質疑蓬佩奧有否對逝去的生命表達同情，有否為拯救生命而作出努力，指出大疫當前，無所作為、草芥人命才是真正的無情，才是對人權的真正蔑視。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568550-20210104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568550-20210104.htm&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=24941b4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568550-20210104.htm&h=5d76b033\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568550-20210104.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3a445b61ab885d183bf19be87dbcfe9dae914c99","tid":2352770,"uid":41545,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"美國：丫屌你老母你個仆街提醒我兩筆數都要同你計清計楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10340a72aaffb3a96cb2fd6d35f385cf708958dc","tid":2352770,"uid":8308,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母仲好意思提"},{"pid":"5bad1525319bda04da4aa870ba8e40670afc53a0","tid":2352770,"uid":62226,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:58:50.000Z","msg":"分化狗，block"},{"pid":"d1b9624be9fb3e0c716ebcb76189b3d9e5e92fde","tid":2352770,"uid":83582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:59:05.000Z","msg":"why